0.1 Visualización 1: Chord diagram

df<-read.csv("./airline_dec_2008_50k.csv",header=T,sep=",")
# Filtrar datos con distancia mayor a 1000 millas
df_clean <- df[df$Distance > 2500, ]
chordDiagram(x= df_clean[,c("Origin", "Dest")]
             )

0.2 Visualización 2: Area Chart

df_coal<-read.csv("./annual-coal-consumption-by-country-1980-2009-2_v4.csv",header=T,sep=",")
# stacked area chart
ggplot(df_coal, aes(x=Año, y=Consumo, fill=pais)) + 
    geom_area()

0.3 Visualización 3: Waffle Chart

waffle(c('Africa' = 103/10, 'Eurasia' = 254/10, 'Asia & Oceania' = 1300/10, 'Europe' = 500/10,'North America' = 641/10  ), rows = 10, size = 0.5,
       colors = c("deepskyblue", "red1", "forestgreen", "gold", "black"),
       title = 'Consumo de Carbón por los principales continentes última década (mill toneladas)', legend_pos="bottom")
